title.description: Change the way a dashboard name appears to users

layout.description: Define the way that the dashboard will place elements (tile | static | grid | newspaper)

crossfilter_enabled.description: Enable or disable cross-filtering for a dashboard

description.description: Add a description that can be viewed in the Dashboard Details panel or in a folder set to list view

preferred_slug.description: Custom URL slug for the dashboard

enable_viz_full_screen.description: Define whether dashboard viewers can see dashboard tiles in full-screen and expanded views

extends.description: Base the LookML dashboard on another LookML dashboard

extension.description: Require that the dashboard is extended by another dashboard

rows.description: Define the elements that should go into each row of a layout: grid dashboard

elements.description: Define the elements that should go into a row of a layout: grid dashboard

height.description: Define the height of a row for a layout: grid dashboard

tile_size.description: Define the size of a tile for a layout: tile dashboard

width.description: Define the width of the dashboard for a layout: static dashboard

refresh.description: Set the interval on which dashboard elements will automatically refresh (seconds | minutes | hours | days)

auto_run.description: Determine whether dashboards run automatically when initially opened or reloaded

filters_bar_collapsed.description: Set the dashboard filter bar as default collapsed or expanded

filters_location_top.description: Position the filters bar at the top of the dashboard

embed_style.description: Customize the appearance of an embedded dashboard

background_color.description: Sets the color of the background of an embedded dashboard

show_title.description: Specifies whether the embedded dashboard title is visible to users

title_color.description: Sets the color of the title of an embedded dashboard

show_filters_bar.description: Specifies whether the embedded dashboard filters are visible to users

tile_background_color.description: Sets the color of the background of all tiles on an embedded dashboard

tile_text_color.description: Sets the color of text on all tiles on an embedded dashboard

text_tile_text_color.description: Sets the color of text on all text tiles on an embedded dashboard

elements.description: Define the elements that will make up a dashboard

title.description: Display title for the dashboard element

name.description: Internal name identifier for the element

note_state.description: State of any notes attached to the element

model.description: Model name for the data source

explore.description: Explore name for the data source

fields.description: Array of field names to display

limit.description: Maximum number of rows to display

column_limit.description: Maximum number of columns to display

show_view_names.description: Show view names in column headers

show_row_numbers.description: Show row numbers in the grid

size_to_fit.description: Automatically size columns to fit content

limit_displayed_rows.description: Limit the number of displayed rows

enable_conditional_formatting.description: Enable conditional formatting for the grid

conditional_formatting_include_nulls.description: Include null values in conditional formatting

collection_id.description: ID of the color collection to use

palette_id.description: ID of the color palette within the collection

show_single_value_title.description: Show title for single value elements
